Command.Statement: with set [measureSet] as '{[Measures].[VALUE_THB]}' set [TIMEFilterSet] as '{[TIME].[All TIMEs].[2020], [TIME].[All TIMEs].[2021], [TIME].[All TIMEs].[2022], [TIME].[All TIMEs].[2023], [TIME].[All TIMEs].[2024], [TIME].[All TIMEs].[2025]}' set [TIMECalculatedSet] as '{[TIME].[All TIMEs].[(Total)]}' set [set_2_set] as '{Hierarchize(Distinct(Union([TIMEFilterSet], [TIMECalculatedSet])))}' set [columnHierarchiesSet] as '{Filter([set_2_set], not (isEmpty([Measures].[VALUE_THB])))}' set [columnSet] as '{Crossjoin([columnHierarchiesSet], [measureSet])}' set [set_0_set] as '{Union({[COUNTRY].[All COUNTRYs]}, [COUNTRY].levels(1).AllMembers)}' set [rowHierarchiesSet] as '{Filter([set_0_set], not (isEmpty([Measures].[VALUE_THB])))}' set [rowSet] as '{[rowHierarchiesSet]}' member [TIME].[All TIMEs].[(Total)] as 'Aggregate({[TIME].[All TIMEs].[2020],[TIME].[All TIMEs].[2021],[TIME].[All TIMEs].[2022],[TIME].[All TIMEs].[2023],[TIME].[All TIMEs].[2024],[TIME].[All TIMEs].[2025]})' Select NON EMPTY [columnSet] DIMENSION PROPERTIES PARENT_UNIQUE_NAME, HIERARCHY_UNIQUE_NAME, MEMBER_TYPE ON COLUMNS , NON EMPTY [rowSet] DIMENSION PROPERTIES PARENT_UNIQUE_NAME, HIERARCHY_UNIQUE_NAME, MEMBER_TYPE ON ROWS FROM [TRADE] CELL PROPERTIES VALUE
